<div class="page" id="p5">
  <div class="tag">Practice 2</div>
  <h1>Make One Sentence ✍️</h1>
  <p class="sub">Join the two sentences into one using a relative clause. Write your answer, then click Show Answers.</p>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="clb">Combine using who / which / where / when / whose / that</div>
